itle":"Abu Yazid on Will: I want not to want anything in the world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 26, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Qayyim reported: It was said to Abu Yazid, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cWhat do you want?\u201d Abu Yazid said, \u201cI want not to want.\u201d Ibn al-Qayyim said, \u201cHe wanted the lower-self to be cut off from its aims\u2026 so he guarded his will and restricted it from\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32337,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/19\/angels-guided-humility-kibr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34574,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Angels: Guided by humility, humbled by arrogance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no human being but that over his head are reins in the hands of an angel. If he is humble, it is said to the angel: Raise up his reins! If he is haughty,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9944,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/24\/abu-huraira-speck-plank-eye\/","url_meta":{"origin":34574,"position":2},"title":"Abu Huraira on Hypocrisy: You ignore the plank in your own eye?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Yazid ibn al-Asim reported: Abu Huraira, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cOne of you looks at the speck in his brother\u2019s eye while he ignores the plank or log in his own eye.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 592 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0645\u0651\u0650 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0623\u0628\u0648\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/06\/abdullah-except-dishonesty\/","url_meta":{"origin":34574,"position":3},"title":"Abdullah on Faith: Believers have many temperaments, except dishonesty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Yazid reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe believer may have all kinds of natural dispositions flowing throughout himself, except for treachery and dishonesty.\u201d Source: al-\u012ama\u0304n li-Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u064a\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28987,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/umar-humility-raises-wisdom\/","url_meta":{"origin":34574,"position":4},"title":"Umar on Humility: Allah raises his wisdom if he humbles himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubaydullah ibn \u2018Adi reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said upon the pulpit, \u201cVerily, if a servant humbles himself for Allah Almighty, he will increase his wisdom.\u201d Source: Juz\u2019 fi\u0304hi\u0304 H\u0323adi\u0304th Sufya\u0304n ibn \u2018Uyaynah 24 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1696,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/03\/glory-allah-consume-all-creation\/","url_meta":{"origin":34574,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Allah: Glory of Allah revealed would consume all creation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 3, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty does not sleep, nor is it befitting that He sleeps. He lowers and raises the balance of justice. Deeds ascend to him by night before the work of the day, and deeds ascend\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.ab